{
    "content":{
        "from":"features@sparkpostbox.com",
        "html":"<html>
  <body>
    <h1>SparkPost Email Template Features</h1>
    <p>Insert substitution variables: I like {{flavor}} ice cream.</p>
    <p>Make some content conditional: Your ice cream is {{if flavor == "strawberry"}} pink {{else}} cream{{end}}-colored.</p>
    <p>Iterate through items in a list:
      <ul>
        {{each desserts}}
        <li>{{loop_var}}</li>
        {{end}}
      </ul>
    </p>
    <p>Inserting HTML using variables:
      {{{setMenuHTML}}}
    </p>
    <p>Inserting HTML containing variables:
      {{render_dynamic_content(dynamic_html.setMenuHTMLWithSpecial)}}
    </p>
    <p>Controlling links:
      <ul>
        <li>Named links for reporting: <a data-msys-linkname="SparkPost" href="https://www.sparkpost.com/">SparkPost</a></li>
        <li>Labelling an unsubscribe linke: <a data=msys-unsubscribe="1" href="http://www.example.com/unsubs">unsubscribe</a></li>
        <li>Controlling link tracking for a single link: <a data-msys-clicktrack="0" href="https://www.example.com/">don't track this</a></li>
      </ul>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
",
        "subject":"features",
        "text":"SparkPost Email Template Features

Insert substitution variables: I like {{flavor}} ice cream.

Make some content conditional: Your ice cream is {{if flavor == "strawberry"}} pink {{else}} cream{{end}}-colored.

Iterate through items in a list:
{{each desserts}}
- {{loop_var}}
{{end}}

Inserting text using variables:
{{{setMenuText}}}

Inserting text containing variables:
{{render_dynamic_content(dynamic_plain.setMenuTextWithSpecial)}}

Controlling links:
- Named links for reporting: https://www.sparkpost.com/[[data-msys-linkname="SparkPost"]]

- Labelling an unsubscribe linke: http://www.example.com/unsubs[[data=msys-unsubscribe="1"]]

- Controlling link tracking for a single link: https://www.example.com/[[data-msys-clicktrack="0"]]

"
    },
    "description":"Send email using template: features",
    "recipients":[
        {
            "address":"you@example.sinkhole.sparkpostmail.com"
        }
    ],
    "substitution_data":{
        "desserts":[
            "ice cream",
            "profiteroles",
            "blancmange",
            "bread pudding"
        ],
        "dynamic_html":{
            "setMenuHTMLWithSpecial":"<ol><li><b>Special: {{specialDish}}</b></li><li>Soup</li><li>Steak frites</li><li>Ice cream</li></ol>"
        },
        "dynamic_plain":{
            "setMenuTextWithSpecial":"Special: {{specialDish}}
Soup, Steak frites and Ice cream"
        },
        "flavor":"chocolate",
        "setMenuHTML":"<ol><li><b>Soup</b></li><li>Steak frites</li><li>Ice cream</li></ol>",
        "setMenuText":"-Soup
-Steak frites
-Ice cream",
        "specialDish":"Tête de veau"
    }
}

